Title: Syzygy
Plot: A rare planetary alignment causes strange behavior in the residents of a small town, but particularly in two teenage girls who were born at the exact same moment on that date.
GuestStars: Dana Wheeler-Nicholson, Wendy Benson-Landes, Lisa Robin Kelly, Garry Davey, Ryan Reynolds, Denalda Williams, Gabrielle Miller, Tim Dixon, Ryk Brown, Jeremy Radick, Russell Porter, Jordan Lee Williams
